t%20afford%20to%20pay%20our%20employees%20crazy%20salaries%2C%20but%20I%20hired%20people%20for%20sales%20and%20customer-facing%20roles%20in%20the%20US%2C%20while%20my%20cofounder%20looked%20for%20product%20and%20tech%20staff%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbengaluru-city-tech-hub-water-crisis-traffic-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findia-silicon-valley-bengaluru-under-pressure-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIndia's%20Silicon%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would've%20been%20convenient%20to%20hire%20in%20the%20US%20from%20Seattle%20or%20even%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20but%20Bengaluru%20has%20a%20strong%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-founder-bengaluru-india-silicon-valley-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estartup%20ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20really%20good%20tech%20talent%2C%20including%20developers%2C%20who%20cost%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20they%20would%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20does%20having%20talent%20working%20across%20two%20time%20zones%20keep%20our%20costs%20down%2C%20it%20allows%20our%20operations%20to%20run%20round-the-clock.%20India's%20working%20hours%20overlap%20with%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20South%20East%20Asia%2C%20while%20the%20US%20can%20overlap%20with%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20believe%20we've%20compromised%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20talent%20and%20don't%20treat%20our%20Bengaluru%20location%20as%20an%20outsourcing%20center.%20We%20see%20ourselves%20as%20one%20firm%20across%20time%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20not%20worried%20about%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-100k-h1b-visa-fee-tech-ceo-support-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echanges%20to%20H-1B%20visa%20sponsorships%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it%20won't%20impact%20our%20hiring%20strategy.%20We%20intend%20to%20hire%20local%20employees%20in%20the%20US%20who%20don't%20require%20visa%20sponsorship%2C%20and%20use%20the%20L-1%20visa%20for%20company%20transfers%20for%20moving%20talent%20from%20India%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c466c422-cc8d-4a67-8a3a-1cc73a9c0eb3%5C%22%3EWorking%20in%20different%20time%20zones%20requires%20my%20cofounder%20and%20me%20to%20compromise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mornings%20are%20my%20cofounder's%20evenings%2C%20so%20we%20typically%20have%20early%20morning%20or%20late%20night%20calls%20with%20each%20other.%20But%20after%20working%20in%20consulting%2C%20we're%20used%20to%20long%20hours.%20It%20very%20much%20feels%20like%20we're%20working%20together.%20We%20communicate%20a%20lot%20on%20Zoom%20and%20travel%20to%20meet%20each%20other%20in%20person%20every%20few%20months%20in%20either%20India%20or%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20between%20eight%20and%20nine%20months%20in%20the%20US%20and%20travel%20to%20India%20two%20to%20three%20times%20a%20year.%20I%20have%20family%20in%20India%2C%20so%20I%20combine%20family%20and%20work%20trips%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20super%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fcf5d91a-5b2b-4478-af41-98a4c5991c80%5C%22%3EI'm%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20Seattle%20and%20Bengaluru%20and%20their%20tech%20ecosystems%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20headquarters%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincredibly-lonely-high-paying-tech-job-seattle-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20Seattle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20live%20in%20nearby%20Redmond.%20Seattle's%20blessed%20by%20great%20nature%20trails%20and%20hikes%2C%20but%20also%20a%20very%20vibrant%20tech%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20underdog%20city%20that%20doesn't%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%2C%20but%20the%20Amazons%20and%20Microsofts%20of%20the%20world%20are%20based%20in%20the%20area.%20Seattle%20founders%20like%20to%20joke%20that%20the%20cloudy%20weather%20gives%20you%20no%20other%20option%20but%20to