ll%20has%20concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20leaders'%20main%20concerns%20aren't%20surprising%3A%20Mamdani's%20public%20safety%20plans%20will%20make%20the%20city%20less%20safe%2C%20and%20housing%20proposals%20will%20exacerbate%20the%20city's%20housing%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20in%20housing%2C%20there%20are%20areas%20of%20agreement%2C%20Salem%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20leaders%20criticized%20Mamdani's%20plan%20to%20freeze%20the%20rent%20for%20rent-stabilized%20apartments%2C%20arguing%20it%20would%20worsen%20shortages%2C%20noting%20that%20Mayor%20de%20Blasio%20had%20tried%20rent%20freezes%20that%20failed%20to%20address%20the%20long-term%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20both%20sides%20agree%20the%20long-term%20fix%20is%20boosting%20supply%2C%20Salem%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20between%20the%20business%20community%20and%20Mamdani%20is%20in%20their%20time%20horizon.%20Mamdani's%20rent-freeze%20message%20could%20help%20lower%20rents%20now%20and%20satisfy%20voters%2C%20while%20his%20plans%20for%20zoning%20reform%20and%20building%20200%2C000%20%26quot%3Btruly-affordable%26quot%3B%20apartments%20can%20solve%20the%20deeper%20problem%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20we%20solving%20for%20rent%20prices%20going%20down%20in%20four%20years%3F%20Are%20we%20solving%20for%20rent%20prices%20going%20down%20today%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Salem.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20if%20you're%20solving%20for%20rent%20prices%20going%20down%20today%2C%20supply%20is%20not%20going%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20public%20safety%2C%20Salem%20said%20the%20announcement%20that%20Mamdani%20would%20seek%20to%20keep%20Jessica%20Tisch%20on%20as%20NYPD%20commissioner%20has%20helped%20alleviate%20fears%20that%20the%20city%20would%20become%20more%20dangerous%20under%20Mayor%20Mamdani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20leaders%20also%20wanted%20to%20know%20how%20Mamdani's%20new%20Department%20of%20Community%20Safety%2C%20which%20would%20deploy%20civilian%20mental%20health%20responders%20to%20subway%20stations%20and%20to%20answer%20some%20emergency%20calls%2C%20would%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20a%20McDonald's%20owner%20in%20a%20tough%20neighborhood%20gets%20somebody%20coming%20in%20causing%20trouble%2C%26quot%3B%20Salem%20said.%20%26quot%3BDo%20they%20call%20911%20and%20get%20a%20mental%20health%20worker%20rather%20than%20a%20police%20officer%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%2C%20Salem%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20is%20that%20these%20changes%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Badditive%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20mental%20health%20workers%20will%20join%20%26quot%3Balongside%2C%20not%20replacing%20the%20officers%20on%20the%20scene.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20he%20said%2C%20taxes%20don't%20come%20up%20as%20a%20big%20fear.%20CEOs%20told%20them%20they're%20willing%20to%20pay%20more%20if%20they%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20that%20New%20York%20is%20a%20better%20place%20to%20live%20as%20a%20result.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20that%20Tisch%20was%20staying%20on%20helped%20alleviate%20some%20of%20the%20more%20intangible%20fears%20of%20the%20city's%20business%20elite%2C%20too%2C%20said%20Salem%2C%20such%20as%20Mamdani's%20inexperience%20or%20his%20ideological%20commitments%20to%20socialism%2C%20or%20to%20the%20pro-Palestine%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20appointing%20someone%20with%20extensive%20experience%20that's%20guaranteed%20to%20frustrate%20his%20most%20progressive%20supporters%2C%20Salem%20said%20he%20began%20to%20prove%20himself%20to%20some%20business%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Salem%2C%20who%20doesn't%20consider%20himself%20a%20socialist%20but%20instead%20a%20%26quot%3Bpro-responsible%20capitalist%2C%26quot%3B%20also%20said%20that%20he%20would%20try%20to%20get%20CEOs%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20specific%20disagreements%20with%20Mamdani's%20policies%2C%20rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessin