m%2Fhedge-funds-business-development-executive-hiring-talent-war-citadel-walleye-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatt%20Giannini%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20the%20top%20equities%20BD%20exec%20and%20whom%20some%20industry%20insiders%20consider%20among%20the%20best%20in%20the%20role%2C%20left%20last%20October%20for%20a%20role%20as%20Walleye's%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20long-short%20equity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel%20has%20hired%20reinforcements%20for%20its%20senior%20BD%20ranks%20as%20well.%20Former%20Point72%20chief%20fundraiser%20Laura%20Sterner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Feurope%2Fcitadel-hires-sterner-role-global-equities-business-2025-09-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20brought%20on%20in%20September%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fill%20Topkins'%20role%20as%20the%20head%20of%20BD%20for%20the%20firm's%20Global%20Equities%20unit%2C%20which%20is%20run%20by%20onetime%20Point72%20PM%20Justin%20Lubell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustas%20Povilenas%20has%20been%20hired%20as%20head%20of%20BD%20in%20Europe%20for%20the%20Global%20Fixed%20Income%20division%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned%2C%20joining%20from%20BlackRock's%20fund%20of%20funds%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCitadel%20is%20the%20No.%201%20destination%20for%20talent%20in%20our%20industry%2C%20and%20our%20team%20is%20well-positioned%20to%20drive%20the%20firm%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20Citadel%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229753c65a-857f-4b7c-a411-46cc296fb792%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChurn%20amid%20industry%20talent%20war%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20insiders%20who've%20worked%20with%20or%20in%20Citadel's%20BD%20apparatus%20didn't%20identify%20a%20unifying%20reason%20for%20the%20recent%20spate%20of%20departures.%20Several%20were%20terminated%20and%20others%20left%20voluntarily%2C%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel%2C%20accustomed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-generates-top-profits-for-investors-memo-lch-investments-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindustry-leading%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20having%20a%20down%20year%20by%20its%20standards%2C%20returning%205%25%20through%20September%20and%20trailing%20most%20of%20its%20peers.%20Some%20of%20the%20exits%20predate%202025%20performance%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure%20and%20demands%20of%20the%20job%20are%20a%20common%20refrain.%20Citadel%20BD%20execs%20are%20evaluated%20in%20part%20on%20performance%20metrics%20related%20to%20the%20success%20of%20the%20candidates%20they%20introduce%20to%20Citadel's%20business%20leaders%2C%20three%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Citadel%2C%20that's%20not%20unique%20to%20BD%3B%20the%20firm's%20exacting%20reputation%20and%20expectations%20are%20well%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChurn%20is%20also%20a%20common%20byproduct%20when%20a%20new%20executive%20shows%20up.%20Last%20October%2C%20chief%20people%20officer%20Matt%20Jahansouz%20left%20the%20industry%2C%20a%20move%20that%20had%20been%20planned%20for%20months%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%20He%20was%20replaced%20the%20following%20month%20by%20Sjoerd%20Gehring%2C%20a%20former%20Apple%20executive%20with%20an%20extensive%20background%20in%20recruiting%20at%20firms%20such%20as%20Johnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%20and%20Accenture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBD%20execs%20at%20Citadel%20work%20and%20recruit%20for%20business%20unit%20leaders%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Lubell%20in%20Global%20Equities%20or%20Navneet%20Arora%20in%20GQS%20%E2%80%94%20but%20also%20report%20into%20the%20chief%20people%20officer%2C%20the%20company's%20top%20recruiting%20exec.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20whether%20Gehring's%20arrival%20directly%20contributed%20to%20the%20recent%20departures%2C%20some%20of%20which%20were%20in%20the%20works%20before%20or%20shortly%20after%20he%20joined%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20m