0the%20late%20innings%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkey-insights-tech-earnings-alphabet-amazon-apple-meta-microsoft-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethird-quarter%20earnings%20season%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20results%20so%20far%20have%20been%20solid%2C%20with%20two%20stats%20in%20particular%20hinting%20that%20the%20bull%20rally%20will%20continue%20into%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley's%20chief%20stock%20strategist%2C%20Michael%20Wilson%2C%20recently%20wrote%20that%20his%20team%20has%20been%20impressed%20by%20the%20strong%20growth%20in%20both%20sales%20and%20earnings%20per%20share%20from%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20has%20been%20focused%20on%20Big%20Tech%20earnings%20for%20clues%20about%20t%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-spending-on-ai-capex-q3-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehe%20AI%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20Wilson%20noted%20that%20the%20broader%20stats%20coming%20out%20of%20this%20earnings%20season%20have%20implications%20for%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20broader%20market%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20said%20he's%20focused%20on%20two%20things%20in%20particular%3A%20%3Cstrong%3Epositive%20revenue%20surprises%20and%20EPS%20growth.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20encouraged%20by%20the%20sales%20beat%20rate%20in%20earnings%20season%20(%3E2x%20avg.)%20and%20the%20best%20EPS%20growth%20for%20the%20median%20stock%20(11%25)%20in%204%20years%E2%80%94supportive%20of%20our%20call%20that%20a%20new%20cycle%20and%20bull%20market%20began%20in%20April%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22932%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley%20showing%20median%20stock%20EPS%20growth.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6908ee12599d46a4ccc15942%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%202.3%25%20sales%20growth%20may%20not%20seem%20high%2C%20it%20is%20roughly%20twice%20the%20typical%20rate%20of%201.1%25.%20It%20signals%20that%20businesses%20are%20not%20only%20generating%20more%20profit%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20successfully%20selling%20more%20goods%20and%20services%20than%20Wall%20Street%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20said%20that%20the%20median%20companies%20in%20the%20Russell%203000%20index%20reached%2011%25%20EPS%20growth%2C%20almost%20double%20their%20second-quarter%20rate%20of%206%25.%20This%20shows%20that%20profits%20are%20expanding%20across%20many%20sectors%20beyond%20Big%20Tech%2C%20supporting%20Wilson's%20thesis%20that%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Brolling%26quot%3B%20earnings%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20this%20is%20an%20underappreciated%20story%20and%20see%20this%20trend%20continuing%20into%202026%2C%20driving%20a%20broadening%20in%20earnings%20contribution%20across%20major%20and%20secondary%20indices.%20As%20usual%2C%20stocks%20have%20figured%20this%20out%20ahead%20of%20the%20consensus%20forecaster%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20other%20fronts%2C%20Wilson%20said%20that%20the%20trade%20truce%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20last%20week%20has%20%26quot%3Blargely%20diffused%26quot%3B%20trade%20tensions%2C%20which%20is%20positive%20for%20markets.%20However%2C%20he%20added%20that%20there%20are%20lingering%20uncertainties%20around%20interest%20rates%20given%20Jerome%20Powell's%20comments%20at%20last%20week's%20Fed%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20next%206-12%20months%2C%20we%20think%20moderate%20weakness%20in%20lagging%20labor%20data%20and%20the%20administration's%20desire%20to%20%26quot%3Brun%20it%20hot%26quot%3B%20will%20lead%20to%20an%20accommodative%20monetary%20policy%20backdrop%20even%20as%20nominal%20growth%20improves%2C%20but%20there%20is%20uncertainty%20around%20the%20pace%20and%20ma