tion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f459c6f-5204-4f13-86fa-113826199fe7%5C%22%3EThe%20three%20steps%20of%20intentional%20career%20design%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20increase%20your%20chances%20of%20landing%20the%20job%20you%20want%2C%20there%20are%20three%20steps%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22659e1c38-c858-49d2-8a20-2843455f14d4%5C%22%3EStep%201%3A%20the%20%26quot%3Bmillion-dollar%26quot%3B%20impact%20and%20your%20seven-figure%20signature%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20%24100%2C000%20you%20want%20to%20make%2C%20you%20need%20to%20have%20at%20least%20seven%20figures%20of%20impact%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiter-who-has-written-over-700-resumes-best-advice-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyour%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20say%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%26quot%3B%20because%20right%20now%2C%20the%20more%2C%20the%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20could%20include%20revenue%20growth%2C%20an%20increase%20in%20reputation%2C%20reach%2C%20or%20profit%20margins%2C%20or%20risk%20reduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20job%20you%20do%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20support%20role%20or%20if%20you're%20on%20the%20executive%20team.%20You%20need%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20you%20help%20a%20company%20save%20or%20make%20money.%20A%20company%20will%20hire%20someone%20when%20there%20is%20a%20reason%20for%20it%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20a%20business%20case%20with%20an%20expected%20commercial%20benefit%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20seven-figure%20signature%20needs%20to%20be%20aligned%20with%20what's%20happening.%20The%20job%20market%20is%20in%20flux%2C%20so%20if%20you're%20marketing%20a%20skillset%20that's%20becoming%20antiquated%2C%20that's%20a%20problem%3B%20you're%20not%20competing%20in%20the%20current%20labor%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c842fbb-ac26-4194-8dad-8009b84b32ef%5C%22%3EStep%202%3A%20Communicate%20your%20impact%20clearly%20and%20quickly%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20step%20is%20then%20what%20I%20call%20%26quot%3BMe%20Inc.%26quot%3B%20marketing%20materials.%20I%20run%20%26quot%3BLindsay%20Inc.%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20you%20run%20%26quot%3BYou%20Inc.%26quot%3B%20That%20means%20the%20tools%20we%20use%20to%20market%20our%20business%20need%20to%20be%20on%20point.%20Your%20marketing%20materials%20need%20to%20show%20proof%2C%20impact%2C%20and%20quantifiable%20results%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20you've%20got%20about%20six%20seconds%20to%20make%20an%20impression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20often%20look%20at%20your%20LinkedIn%20profile%20before%20giving%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhr-consultant-shares-common-interview-mistakes-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20your%20profile%20needs%20to%20model%20the%20same%20story%20as%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20but%20with%20a%20few%20other%20features%2C%20like%20a%20profile%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20talk%20about%20the%20bias%20that%20it%20brings%2C%20but%20a%20profile%20photo%20on%20your%20LinkedIn%20page%20drives%20more%20views.%20Humans%20quickly%20interpret%20profile%20photos%20and%20make%20unconscious%20decisions%2C%20often%20influenced%20by%20some%20biases.%20You%20want%20to%20use%20that%20bias%20to%20frame%20yourself%20as%20warm%2C%20welcoming%2C%20competent%2C%20influential%2C%20or%20likable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20that%20really%20matters%20is%20your%20headline%2C%20both%20for%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20your%20LinkedIn.%20Make%20sure%20your%20headline%20classifies%20what%20you%20do%20%E2%80%94%20the%20level%2C%20the%20scope%2C%20the%20impact.%20It%20should%20also%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20secret%20sauce%2C%20something%20that%20you%20do%20that's%20uniquely%20you%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20candidate%20differentiation%20strategy.%20Just%20like%20a%20news%20headline%20should%20hook%20the%20reader's%20attention%20and%20make%20them%20want%20to%20read%20more%2C%20your%20LinkedIn%20headline%20should%20try%20to%20get%20them%20to%20go%20past%20the%20fold%20and%20scroll%20down%20on%20the%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20LinkedIn%20summary%20should%20show%20that%20seven-figure%20signature.%20It%20should%20help%20potential%20employers%20understand%20in%20just%20a%20few%20seconds%20that%20you're%20somebody%20worth%20spending%20at%20least%2030%20minutes%20with%20on%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22412697aa-dd00-4d54-a5b9-072f05859391%5C%22%3EStep%203%3A%20Elevate%20your%20authority%20and%20influence%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20is%20the%20candidate%20choice%20framework%2C%20which%20is%20about%20visibility%20and%20understanding%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhidden-job-market-rejection-offer-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehidden%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20How%20can%20you%20increase%20the%20visibility%20of%20your%20LinkedIn%20profile%20to%20recruiters%20and%20attract%20more%20views%3F%20You%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Flindsaymustain%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengage%20on%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Engaging%20strategically%20with%20the%20right%20information%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20being%20a%20top%201%25%20talent.%20You%20should%20be%20sharing%2C%20commenting%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flara-sophie-bothur-tips-for-being-a-corporate-tech-influencer-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20your%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20so%20important%20to%20increase%20your%20influence%2C%20visibility%2C%20and%20perceived%20authority%20because%20recruiters%20aren't%20waiting%20for%20you%20to%20find%20our%20job%20openings%20and%20apply.%20When%20I%20was%20a%20recruiter%2C%20I%20went%20through%20the%20fair%20consideration%20process%2C%20but%20generally%2C%20before%20a%20job%20got%2