In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.salesforce.com%2Fplus%2Fexperience%2Fdreamforce_2024%2Fseries%2Fbest_of_dreamforce_2024%2Fepisode%2Fepisode-s1e1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20sleek%20demo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20showed%20how%20luxury%20retailer%20Saks%20Fifth%20Avenue%20was%20using%20Salesforce's%20new%20flagship%20AI%20software%20Agentforce%20to%20create%20%26quot%3BSophie%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20charming%2C%20patient%20customer%20service%20representative.%20A%20Salesforce%20executive%20dialed%20a%20Saks%20hotline%2C%20the%20chipper-voiced%20Sophie%20picked%20up%2C%20and%20then%20deftly%20recommended%20a%20sweater%20based%20on%20his%20order%20history%20and%20talked%20through%20shipping%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESophie%20reflected%20the%20promise%20of%20AI%20agents%2C%20which%20have%20had%20no%20bigger%20booster%20than%20Marc%20Benioff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20unveiling%20Agentforce%2C%20the%20Salesforce%20CEO%20wrote%20an%20essay%20in%20Time%20Magazine%2C%20which%20he%20owns%2C%20declaring%20that%20agents%20would%20unleash%20%26quot%3Ba%20revolution%20that%20will%20fundamentally%20redefine%20how%20humans%20work%2C%20live%2C%20and%20connect%20with%20one%20another%20from%20this%20point%20forward.%26quot%3B%20And%20he%20would%20lead%20this%20revolution%2C%20he%20boasted.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-benioff-salesforce-ceo-interview-microsoft-ai-threatens-crm-lead-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Sophie%20was%20already%20live%20on%20Saks'%20website.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20what%20our%20customers%20are%20able%20to%20do%26quot%3B%20with%20Salesforce's%20AI%20tools%2C%20he%20said%2C%20unlike%20those%20from%20one%20of%20his%20chief%20competitors.%20%26quot%3BMicrosoft%20doesn't%20have%20these%20examples%2C%20actually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20weeks%20after%20Agentforce's%20debut%2C%20Salesforce's%20stock%20surged%20by%20more%20than%2050%25%2C%20peaking%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20last%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20year%20later%2C%20shares%20are%20slumping%20as%20competitors'%20stocks%20keep%20climbing%20higher.%20Some%20Salesforce%20investors%2C%20analysts%2C%20clients%2C%20and%20even%20employees%20say%20Benioff%20may%20have%20placed%20too%20many%20chips%20on%20a%20bet%20that%20is%20yet%20to%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce's%20public%20disclosures%20show%20that%20fewer%20than%20half%20of%20the%20company's%2012%2C500%20Agentforce%20customers%20are%20paying.%20Of%20its%20total%20customers%2C%20less%20than%202%25%20were%20having%20more%20than%2050%20Agentforce%20conversations%20per%20week%20as%20of%20this%20summer%2C%20according%20to%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20internal%20reports.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20Salesforce%20spokesperson%20said%20those%20numbers%20are%20just%20one%20cut%20of%20data%20that%20doesn't%20represent%20actual%20adoption%20or%20how%20the%20tool%20is%20being%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESophie%20is%20also%20not%20live%20as%20it%20debuted%20as.%20Today%2C%20when%20a%20customer%20calls%20Saks'%20hotline%2C%20a%20robotic%20voice%20answers%2C%20and%20responds%20to%20basic%20commands%20before%20transferring%20customers%20to%20a%20human%20representative%20%E2%80%94%20an%20experience%20virtually%20indistinguishable%20from%20the%20technology%20that%20banks%20and%20airlines%20have%20been%20using%20since%20the%201980s.%20In%20August%2C%20Saks%20announced%20it's%20partnering%20with%20Amazon%20and%20AI%20company%20NLX%20on%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnlx.ai%2Fin-the-news%2Fwwd-saks-fifth-avenues-latest-ai-venture-a-virtual-voice-assistant-called-sophie%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20AI-powered%20virtual%20voice%20assistant%20named%20'Sophie.'%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20Business%20is%20today's%20must-read%20story%20on%20what%20the%20forces%20shaping%20business%2C%20tech%2C%20and%20innovation%20mean%20for%20you.%20Each%20piece%20delivers%20insights%20to%20help%20you%20make%20smarter%20career%2C%20money%2C%20and%20life%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Evans%2C%20an%20executive%20vice%20president%20at%20Salesforce%20who%20heads%20Agentforce%2C%20tells%20Business%20Insider%20he%20can't%20%26quot%3Bcomment%20on%20exactly%20what's%20happening%20with%20Saks%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20%26quot%3Bactual%20tangible%20return%20on%20investment%20value%20is%20being%20created%20across%20thousands%20of%20our%20customers.%26quot%3B%20A%20company%20spokesperson%20adds%20that%20Salesforce%20customers%20have%20used%20Agentforce%20in%20more%20than%203%20billion%20instances%20to%20date%20and%20that%20customers%20from%20Williams%20Sonoma%20to%20Singapore%20Airlines%20to%20the%20South%20American%20retailer%20Falabella%20%26quot%3Bare%20seeing%20value%20as%20they%20ramp%20up%20use%20cases.%26quot%3B%20PepsiCo%20transformation%20officer%20Athina%20Kanioura%20tells%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20is%20using%20Agentforce%20to%20help%201.5%20million%20retail%20stores%20manage%20their%20orders%20of%20its%20products%20and%20is%20targeting%205%20million%20stores%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20struggles%20with%20agents%20and%20generative%20AI%20in%20general%20aren't%20unique%20to%20Salesforce.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmlq.ai%2Fmedia%2Fquarterly_decks%2Fv0.1_State_of_AI_in_Business_2025_Report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMIT%20report%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20despite%20%2430%20billion%20to%20%2440%20billion%20in%20enterprise%20spending%20on%20generative%20AI%2C%2095%25%20of%20organizations%20report%20no%20return%20on%20investment.%20The%20management%20consultancy%20Gartner%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gartner.com%2Fen%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2F2025-06-25-gartner-predicts-over-40-percent-of-agentic-ai-projects-will-be-canceled-by-end-of-2027%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredicted%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20agentic%20AI%20projects%20will%20be%20canceled%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20end%20of%202027%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bescalating%20costs%2C%20unclear%20business%20value%2C%20or%20inadequate%20risk%20controls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20Salesforce%20is%20necessarily%20behind%20competitors%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20agents%2C%20says%20Gil%20Luria%2C%20head%20of%20technology%20research%20at%20D.A.%20Davidson.%20It's%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bbet%20the%20farm%26quot%3B%20on%20an%20early%20and%20unproven%20technology%20and%20neglected%20their%20core%20business.%20%26quot%3BSalesforce%20became%20so%20focused%20on%20their%20AI%20product%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20business%20%E2%80%A6%20was%20decelerating%20very%20sharply%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20paying%20too%20much%20attention%20to%20this%20new%20thing%20and%20not%20enough%20to%20what%20got%20them%20there.%26quot%3B%20A%20Salesforce%20spokesperson%20said%20Agentforce%20is%20part%20of%20its%20core%20business%20and%20%26quot%3Benhances%20every%20Salesforce%20application%20by%20making%20it%20agentic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSalesforce%20is%20uniquely%20vulnerable%20because%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20cloud%20business%20to%20fall%20back%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20senior%20employee%20says.%20%26quot%3BMicrosoft%20has%20plenty%20to%20fall%20back%20on%2C%20Amazon%20has%20plenty%20to%20fall%20back%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgentforce%20is%20Salesforce's%20No.%201%20priority%2C%20according%20to%20a%20draft%20of%20the%20company's%20annual%20strategic%20plan%20for%20its%20upcoming%20fiscal%20year.%20The%20annual%20plan%20is%20typically%20finalized%20by%20February.%20%26quot%3BWin%20the%20enterprise%20agent%20wars%26quot%3B%20is%20listed%20as%20the%20first%20method%20of%20success%20for%20Salesforce%2C%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20agentic%20enterprise%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20internal%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20is%20down%20more%20than%2020%25%20year%20to%20date%2C%20while%20peers%20like%20Oracle%20and%20Microsoft%20are%20up%20around%2055%25%20and%2024%25%2C%20respectively.%20Salesforce's%20revenue%20growth%20rate%20earlier%20this%20year%20slowed%20to%20single%20digits%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20its%20history%20as%20a%20public%20company.%20Another%20pressure%20point%3A%20An%20activist%20investor%20that%20pushed%20Salesforce%20into%20significant%20cost-cutting%20in%202022%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(before%20selling%20many%20of%20its%20shares)%20increased%20its%20stake%20by%20nearly%2050%25%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stakes%20are%20high%20for%20every%20Big%20Tech%20company%20in%20the%20agent%20wars.%20For%20Salesforce%2C%20losing%20may%20be%20catastrophic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20company%2C%20some%20current%20and%20former%20employees%20say%20there's%20been%20constant%20struggle%20for%20the%20teams%20scrambling%20to%20deliver%20on%20Benioff's%20public%20promises%20of%20what%20their%20AI%20products%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemos%20of%20software%20to%20customers%20or%20at%20Dreamforce%2C%20Salesforce's%20annual%20blowout%20conference%2C%20often%20showcase%20concepts%20that%20are%20months%20or%20years%20away%2C%20and%20the%20company%20sometimes%20shifts%20direction%20before%20these%20products%20are%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%2C%20very%20difficult%20%E2%80%94%20even%20for%20people%20working%20on%20the%20products%20%E2%80%94%20to%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20what%20we%20say%20in%20a%20demo%2C%20what's%20on%20a%20road%20map%2C%20and%20what's%20actually%20in%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20senior%20employee%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20full-time%20job%20just%20figuring%20that%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20insiders%20say%20the%20current%20version%20of%20Agentforce%2C%20requires%20significant%20technical%20skill%20from%20Salesforce's%20clients.%20Kristi%20Valente%2C%20a%20director%20of%20sales%20operation%20for%20a%20large%20appliance%20and%20electronics%20distributor%2C%20has%20been%20a%20Salesforce%20administrator%20helping%20companies%20use%20its%20software%20since%202008.%20She%20says%20the%20Agentforce%20demo%20her%20company%20received%20made%20it%20look%20like%20the%20technology%20was%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20set%20up%20and%20less%20expensive%20to%20use.%20Her%20company%20purchased%20it%20in%20April%20and%20has%20yet%20to%20set%20it%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marc%20Benioff%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690901b6599d46a4ccc15b73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarc%20Benioff%3Cp%3EJessica%20Christian%2FSan%20Francisco%20Chronicle%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20a%20normal%20business%20with%20normal%20admins%2C%20you%20do%20not%20have%20the%20expertise%20to%20set%20this%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hired%20a%20consultant%20and%20even%20the%20consultant%20is%20confused.%20It's%20too%20new%20for%20anyone%20to%20be%20an%20expert.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20a%20Salesforce%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20since%20launching%20Agentforce%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe've%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20complexities%20of%20building%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20committed%20to%20partnering%20with%20our%20customers%20as%20they%20embark%20on%20their%20technical%20journeys%20to%20becoming%20agentic%20enterprises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20learning%20not%20every%20agent%20or%20use%20case%20is%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Evans%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Agentforce.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20agents%20haven't%20gone%20to%20scale%20because%20prompts%20alone%20are%20not%20enough.%20You%20need%20more.%26quot%3B%20For%20example%2C%20Salesforce%20has%20learned%20clients%20may%20not%20want%20an%20agent%20to%20be%20as%20creative%20as%20a%20chatbot%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20answering%20direct%20questions%20from%20customers%2C%20like%20how%20to%20process%20a%20return%20for%20an%20online%20order.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20Salesforce%20has%20updated%20Agentforce%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Breasoning%20engine%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20agent's%20answers%20and%20behaviors%20are%20more%20predictable%20and%20reliable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Salesforce's%20own%20salespeople%20said%20they%20struggled%20to%20grasp%20how%20the%20AI%20product%20they're%20selling%20works%20or%20what%20it%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%20required%20Agentforce%20training%20for%20salespeople%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20build%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20concierge%20agent%20at%20a%20fictitious%20hotel%20chain%20that%20could%20help%20a%20patron%20with%20things%20like%20booking%20a%20restaurant%20or%20renting%20beach%20chairs.%20Agentforce%20in%20one%20of%20those%20trainings%20required%20a%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20amount%20of%20work%26quot%3B%20even%20to%20set%20up%20basic%20functions%20like%20dinner%20reservations%2C%20an%20employee%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20training%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20who%20took%20that%20training%20knows%20Agentforce%20isn't%20ready%20for%20primetime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20invest%20in%20comprehensive%2C%20hands-on%20Agentforce%20training%20for%20all%2075%2C000%2B%20of%20our%20employees%20because%20we%20recognize%20the%20significant%20shift%20that%20large%20language%20models%20represent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Salesforce%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20response%20to%20the%20complaint.%20%26quot%3BThis%20new%20software%20environment%20is%20fundamentally%20different%20from%20traditional%20design%2C%20which%20is%20why%20change%20management%20and%20knowledge%20transfer%20have%20never%20been%20more%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EKash%20Rangan%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20top%20software%20analyst%2C%20said%20at%20a%20briefing%20following%20the%20investment%20bank's%20technology%20conference%20in%20September%20that%20analysts%20in%20general%20are%20giving%20%26quot%3Bzero%20credibility%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20optimistic%20comments%20from%20software%20companies%20like%20Salesforce%20and%20executives%20like%20Benioff%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Rangan%20said%20of%20Agentforce.%20%26quot%3BIt%20needs%20to%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERangan%20added%20that%20Benioff%2C%20prone%20to%20grandiose%20predictions%20and%20bullish%20forecasts%2C%20was%20more%20measured%20and%20not%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20optimistic%26quot%3B%20at%20Goldman's%20conference.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20in%20the%20fight%2C%20and%20he's%20being%20realistic%20about%20where%20they%20are%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Rangan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%20note%20of%20sobriety%2C%20and%20despite%20Agentforce's%20struggles%2C%20Benioff%20has%20leaned%20into%20his%20signature%20quality%3A%20Extravagance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20same%20Goldman%20talk%2C%20Benioff%20discussed%20an%20ambitious%20target%20for%20Salesforce%3A%20%24100%20billion%20in%20annual%20revenue%2C%20nearly%20three%20times%20the%20revenue%20for%20its%20most%20recent%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20grandiosity%20continued%20a%20month%20later%20at%20Dreamforce%20%E2%80%94%20the%20greatest%2C%20and%20most%20surreal%20show%20in%20SaaS%20%E2%80%94%20a%20three-day%20jamboree%20sprawling%20across%20downtown%20San%20Francisco%20that's%20part%20Davos%2C%20part%20Disney%20World%2C%20part%20Radisson%20banquet%20hall%2C%20part%20Burning%20Man%2C%20and%20entirely%20Benioff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dreamforce%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690901f3599d46a4ccc15b79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDreamforce%3Cp%3EJessica%20Christian%2FSan%20Francisco%20Chronicle%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conference%2C%20which%2050%2C000%20people%20attended%20and%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-18-difficult-months-at-salesforce-2023-4%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20executive%20once%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20costs%20Salesforce%20around%20%24100%20million%20per%20year%2C%20is%20studded%20with%20happy%20hours%2C%20concerts%2C%20celebrities%2C%20and%20even%20mascots.%20Signs%20heralded%20Gen%20Z-coded%20slogans%20like%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20an%20agentic%20aura%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDreamforce%2C%20it's%20a%20vibe.%26quot%3B%20Movie%20star%20Matthew%20McConnaughey%2C%20whom%20Salesforce%20pays%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-reportedly-paying-mcconaughey-millions-despite-layoffs-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20%2410%20million%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20director%2C%26quot%3B%20held%20a%20session%20where%20he%20read%20poetry%20with%20journalist%20Maria%20Shriver.%20A%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20guest%26quot%3B%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20Trump's%20AI%20czar%20David%20Sacks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdavidsacks%2Fstatus%2F1978292299231621448%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20posted%20a%20photo%20with%20Benioff%20kissing%20him%20on%20the%20cheek%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20was%20a%20gift%20shop%20where%20people%20lined%20up%20to%20buy%20plushies%20of%20one%20of%20Salesforce's%20mascots%2C%20%26quot%3BCodey%20the%20Bear%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20copies%20of%20Benioff's%202019%20biography%20%26quot%3BTrailblazer.%26quot%3B%20There%20was%20a%20Metallica%20concert.%20There%20was%20a%20Hawaiian%20conch-blowing%20ceremony.%20Gold%20sequined%20sweatshirts%20were%20handed%20out%20to%20at%20least%20one%20attendee%20in%20an%20annual%20tradition%20for%20achievements%20in%20the%20community%20of%20people%20who%20use%20Salesforce.%20%26quot%3BI%20hate%20that%20I'm%20in%20a%20cult%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20Salesforce%20customer%20said%20while%20describing%20this%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Hoodie%26quot%3B%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDreamforce%20is%20a%20marketing%20event%2C%20it%20is%20a%20sales%20event%2C%20not%20an%20engineering%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20senior%20employee%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20to%20create%20hype%20and%20invite%20big%20customers%20and%20take%20them%20out%20to%20parties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Benioff's%20AI%20agent-focused%20keynote%20address%2C%20his%20salesmanship%20was%20on%20full%20display.%20He%20paused%20his%20speech%20several%20times%20to%20shake%20hands%20with%20celebrities%20like%20musician%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwill.i.am%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewill.i.am%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20titans%20of%20business%20like%20Michael%20Dell.%20He%20talked%20about%20the%20death%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bclose%20personal%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20famed%20primatologist%20Jane%20Goodall%2C%20and%20quipped%20to%20a%20PepsiCo%20executive%20in%20attendance%20how%20much%20his%20friend%20%26quot%3BMatthew%26quot%3B%20(McConnaughey)%20loves%20Doritos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20company%20has%20not%20been%20%26quot%3Bperfect%26quot%3B%20in%20rolling%20out%20the%20Agentforce%20product.%20Later%2C%20at%20a%20briefing%20for%20reporters%2C%20Benioff%20shut%20down%20a%20question%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20adoption%20of%20Agentforce.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20fastest-growing%20product%20in%20our%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20never%20been%20a%20faster-growing%20product.%20That%20we%20have%20that%20much%20already%20is%20way%20beyond%20anything%20we%20could%20have%20expected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Dreamforce%2C%20the%20company%20also%20hosted%20its%20first%20investor%20day%20in%20three%20years.%20Benioff%20took%20the%20stage%20with%20the