Business%20leaders%20like%20Nvidia's%20Jensen%20Huang%20say%20companies%20could%20have%20armies%20of%20bots.%20But%20they%20come%20with%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20features%20of%20computer%20security%20in%20general%20is%2C%20often%20it's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20cat-and-mouse%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joelle%20Pineau%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B20VC%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20ingenuity%20in%20terms%20of%20breaking%20into%20systems%2C%20and%20then%20you%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20ingenuity%20in%20terms%20of%20building%20defenses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20AI%20agents%20may%20impersonate%20entities%20that%20they%20don't%20%26quot%3Blegitimately%20represent%26quot%3B%20and%20take%20actions%20on%20behalf%20of%20these%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20infiltrating%20banking%20systems%20and%20so%20on%2C%20I%20do%20think%20we%20have%20to%20be%20quite%20lucid%20about%20this%2C%20develop%20standards%2C%20develop%20ways%20to%20test%20for%20that%20in%20a%20very%20rigorous%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohere%20was%20founded%20in%202019%20and%20focuses%20on%20building%20for%20other%20businesses%2C%20not%20for%20consumers.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcohere-aidan-gomez-deepseek-ai-r1-businesses-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECanadian%20AI%20startup%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20competes%20with%20foundational%20model%20providers%20such%20as%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20Mistral%2C%20and%20counts%20Dell%2C%20SAP%2C%20and%20Salesforce%20among%20its%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPineau%20worked%20at%20Meta%20from%202017%20until%20she%20joined%20Cohere%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Her%20most%20recent%20role%20at%20the%20tech%20giant%20was%20vice%20president%20of%20AI%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday's%20podcast%2C%20Pineau%20added%20that%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20reduce%20impersonation%20risks%20%26quot%3Bdramatically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20run%20your%20agent%20completely%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20web.%20You're%20reducing%20your%20risk%20exposure%20significantly.%20But%20then%20you%20lose%20access%20to%20some%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20use%20case%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20you%20actually%20need%2C%20there's%20different%20solutions%20that%20may%20be%20appropriate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohere%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20circles%20dubbed%202025%20as%20the%20year%20of%20AI%20agents%2C%20but%20in%20several%20high-profile%20instances%2C%20the%20technology%20has%20gone%20rogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20June%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-ran-store-anthropic-ai-agent-lessons-learned-middle-managers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexperiment%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BProject%20Vend%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20researchers%20at%20Anthropic%20let%20their%20AI%20manage%20a%20store%20in%20the%20company's%20office%20for%20about%20a%20month%20to%20see%20how%20a%20large%20language%20model%20would%20run%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20quickly%20went%20wrong.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20an%20employee%20jokingly%20requested%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftungsten-cube-sold-on-amazon-sell-for-thousands-crypto-community-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etungsten%20cube%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20crypto%20world's%20favorite%20useless%20heavy%20object%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20AI%2C%20called%20Claudius%2C%20took%20it%20seriously.%20Soon%2C%20the%20fridge%20was%20stocked%20with%20cubes%20of%20metal%2C%20and%20the%20AI%20had%20launched%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecialty%20metals%26quot%3B%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaudius%20priced%20items%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20doi