the%20Google-owned%20platform%20after%20the%20two%20companies%20failed%20to%20negotiate%20a%20new%20contract%20that%20would%20let%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-tv-price-increase-cable-bundle-cord-cutting-sunday-ticket-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYouTube%20TV%20subscribers%3C%2Fa%3E%20watch%20Disney's%20television%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Disney%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20company%20asked%20YouTube%20to%20bring%20back%20ABC%20for%20Tuesday's%20US%20Election%20Day.%20Voters%20head%20to%20the%20polls%20for%20key%20local%20contests%2C%20including%20the%20New%20York%20City%20mayor's%20election%20and%20California's%20Proposition%2050%2C%20which%20decides%20whether%20officials%20can%20redraw%20the%20state's%20congressional%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20in%20putting%20the%20public%20interest%20first%20and%20hope%20YouTube%20TV%20will%20take%20this%20small%20step%20for%20their%20customers%20while%20we%20continue%20to%20work%20toward%20a%20fair%20agreement%2C%26quot%3B%20Disney%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20YouTube%20was%20quick%20to%20decline%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20your%20proposal%20would%20permit%20us%20to%20return%20Disney's%20ABC%20stations%20only%20for%20a%20day%20and%20will%20cause%20customer%20confusion%20among%20those%20who%20may%20briefly%20see%20ABC%20on%20YouTube%20TV%20only%20to%20lose%20it%20again%20shortly%20after%2C%26quot%3B%20YouTube%20said%20in%20a%20Monday%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20news%20viewers%20have%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20other%20options%20for%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20election%20news%20information%20is%20very%20widely%20available%20across%20other%20broadcast%20stations%20and%20news%20networks%20on%20YouTube%20TV%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%20the%20main%20YouTube%20service%2C%20for%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20blog%